Well, loot seems exactly the same.  Gorge EEs are the same as the EK ones in power, unless it is one of the named ones like Lord Svril (there are several named EEs in the Gorge, the only big boss is Xorbb, whom I have never fought).  The named ones are a few levels higher in strength, not much tougher.<br>
<br>
As for bolts:  If you are using the level 20 bolt, you will need to use about 2 or 3 (or an extra DD) to kill regular EEs.  If its Cinder Bolt, regular EEs will often die to one shot of that, sometimes you need to mem a small DD to finish them.  The named ones (cept Xorbb) will die to two Cinder Bolts, or one Cinder Bolt and a Blaze.  <br>
<br>
